1. Residents or Employees of IT Park and Cebu Business Park | Until the end of March 2017, Cebu City Marriott Hotel through its outlet the Garden CafÃ© is offering discounts to any qualifying guests who are (1) residents or employees working within IT Park Lahug, Cebu Business Park, (2) employees of any business process outsourcing company within the Philippines. Walk-ins are also welcome.

2.  If you are celebrating your birthday within the month (February and March), you can avail the 50% off. For validation, at least one ID qualifies (with birthdate) for an entire group to avail of the discounted rate. All you have to do is call us for reservations through (032) 411-5800 for appointments. Walk-ins are also welcome.
